{"tid":2227411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賀一誠：香港列低風險區後考慮恢復澳港往來","createTime":"2020-10-02T18:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T07:33:08.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"adb381dc909a7c71f4ffd20f10f6ce800c1c102b","tid":2227411,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"澳門特區行政長官賀一誠話，會等國家將香港列為低風險區後，考慮恢復兩地人員的正常往來。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，黃金周對澳門經濟復甦比預期慢，政府準備再撥200億澳門元儲備，應付最後一季的公務員、社會福利及教育等開支。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552613-20201001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552613-20201001.htm&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=c788957d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552613-20201001.htm&h=77106e30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552613-20201001.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fbbaba67f5a9aa5b7dab0eaabed88ee7fc304508","tid":2227411,"uid":59461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:33:34.000Z","msg":"日日有人中招係極高風險 唔好往來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b8e92cdc51e3dba285d7098f1e297a74264eb1","tid":2227411,"uid":235754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:35:53.000Z","msg":"永遠唔好往來囉 睇你死先定香港死定"},{"pid":"1191c015a57eefad8fed9819e7fb88c77aef505b","tid":2227411,"uid":300542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:36:36.000Z","msg":"我要中華白海豚就ok 唔使恢復喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bg4Vn4U3Jsg&amp;ab_channel=BBCNews%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBg4Vn4U3Jsg%26ab_channel%3DBBCNews%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=8f1e2a3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bg4Vn4U3Jsg&amp;ab_c